-- audio-transcribe.fl — Audio transcription and meeting intelligence
-- Demonstrates: load audio, Whisper transcription, multi-step analysis
-- Usage: fluent run examples/audio-transcribe.fl
-- Requires: OPENAI_API_KEY (Whisper), ANTHROPIC_API_KEY (analysis)

-- ── Load audio file ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
-- Supports: MP3, WAV, FLAC, OGG, M4A, AAC
-- Replace with your own audio file path.
Let recording be load audio "examples/assets/meeting.mp3".

Output "=== Audio Intelligence Pipeline ===".
Output "".
Output "Audio loaded:".
Output recording.

-- ── Step 1: Transcribe with Whisper ─────────────────────────────────────────
@model(temperature: 0, max_tokens: 4000)
Ask openai/gpt-4o-audio-preview to "Transcribe this audio recording accurately. Include speaker labels if multiple speakers are detected. Format as: SPEAKER_1: ... SPEAKER_2: ..." using audio recording and call the result transcript.

Output "".
Output "=== Transcript ===".
Output transcript.

-- ── Step 2: Extract action items ────────────────────────────────────────────
@model(temperature: 0, max_tokens: 400, format: json)
Ask claude to "Extract all action items from this meeting transcript. Return JSON with: action_items (list of objects with owner, task, deadline if mentioned)." using text transcript and call the result actions.

Output "".
Output "=== Action Items ===".
Output actions.

-- ── Step 3: Identify decisions made ────────────────────────────────────────
@model(temperature: 0, max_tokens: 300)
Ask claude to "List all decisions that were made during this meeting as a numbered list." using text transcript and call the result decisions.

Output "".
Output "=== Decisions Made ===".
Output decisions.

-- ── Step 4: Meeting summary ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
@model(temperature: 0.3, max_tokens: 300)
Ask anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6 to "Write a concise meeting summary in 3-4 sentences. Include what was discussed, what was decided, and what comes next." using text transcript and call the result summary.

Output "".
Output "=== Meeting Summary ===".
Output summary.
